3500552">推出了该剧第七季的开场片段</a>，其中还透露了一些即将发生的冒险故事。</p><p>在其他地方，名为《瑞克和莫蒂：动漫》的衍生作品目前正在开发中。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-opening-theme-rick-and-morty-the-anime-3472493">开场片段于今年早些时候在圣地亚哥动漫展上首次亮相</a>，上映日期尚未公布。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/rick-and-morty-season-seven-trailer-reveals-new-voice-actors-replacing-justin-roiland-3504284">《瑞克和莫蒂》第七季预告片揭示了新的配音演员取代了贾斯汀·罗兰，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《赛博朋克 2077》开发商为《幻影自由》中的反俄言论道歉https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-apologises-for-anti- Russian-comments-found-in-phantom-liberty-3504214?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cyberpunk- 2077-开发者为幻影自由中发现的反俄评论道歉Imogen DonovanTue, 26 Sep 2023 09:18:39 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS5Xbox Series X|Shttps://www.nme.com/?p=3504214 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> CD Projekt Red 此前曾通过慈善捐款表示对乌克兰的支持</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-apologises-for-anti-russian-comments-found-in-phantom-liberty-3504214">《赛博朋克 2077》开发者为《幻影自由》中发现的反俄罗斯评论道歉，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-update-2.0-anti-russian-comments-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cyberpunk-2077"><em>《赛博朋克 2077》</em></a>的 2.0 更新显然在角色扮演游戏的乌克兰本地化中添加了反俄罗斯情绪，而开发商否认事先了解这些声明。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/phantom-liberty-is-a-stunning-swan-song-for-cyberpunk-2077-3500337">《幻影自由》是《赛博朋克 2077》的绝妙绝唱</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/cd-projekt-apologizes-for-anti-russian-dialogue-and-images-in-ukrainian-version-of-cyberpunk-2077-says-it-was-added-without-permission/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PC Gamer</a></em>报道，乌克兰版 2.0 更新包含与俄罗斯在顿巴斯多年冲突后于 2022 年 2 月入侵乌克兰有关的更改。</p><p>其中包括一句针对不可玩的警察角色的台词，该台词是从“难道这些混蛋在荒地里不能咬住它吗？”改来的。到“难道整个俄罗斯都不能在荒地里咬住它吗？” “ <a href="https://twitter.com/TheStanislawski/status/1612851610551554048" target="_blank" rel="noopener">俄罗斯</a>”是一个新形成的词，乌克兰人一直用它来贬义俄罗斯人。</p><p>此外，现在的另一句话是“ <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russian_warship,_go_fuck_yourself" target="_blank" rel="noopener">去你妈的</a>，与船所在的方向相同”，这是乌克兰边防人员对袭击蛇岛的俄罗斯导弹巡洋舰说的话。 </p><figure id="attachment_3503693" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3503693" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3503693" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time.jpg" alt="《赛博朋克 2077：幻影自由》。图片来源：CD Projekt Red。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-release-time-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3503693" class="wp-caption-text"> 《赛博朋克 2077：幻影自由》。图片来源：CD Projekt Red。</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cd-projekt-red">CD Projekt Red</a>表示，他们并没有意识到这些反俄罗斯言论已经出现在游戏中。该公司在<a href="https://t.me/s/cdpr_official" target="_blank" rel="noopener">社交媒体渠道</a>上表示，这些新增内容“并不代表其观点”，也并非来自开发商的任何人。</p><p> “《<em>赛博朋克 2077》</em>的乌克兰本地化版包含一些可能冒犯某些俄罗斯玩家的言论，”CD Projekt Red（通过机器翻译）解释道。 “我们正在努力修复它们并在下一次更新中替换它们。我们对这种情况表示歉意，并正在采取措施确保不再发生这种情况。”</p><p> CD Projekt Red 已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cd-projekt-red-donates-to-humanitarian-organisation-in-support-of-ukraine-3170280">对俄罗斯采取立场</a>，已向位于波兰的人道主义组织 Polska Akcja Humanitarna 捐赠了约 181,000 英镑。</p><p>本次更新的本地化由 SBT Localization 负责，该公司还参与了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii">《博德之门 3》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/darkest-dungeon-2-how-redhook-studios-are-reinventing-their-roguelike-classic-3085987">《黑暗地牢》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/kingdom-come-deliverance">《天国：拯救</a></em>》等游戏的本地化工作。 </p><figure id="attachment_3501142" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3501142" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3501142" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware.jpg" alt="赛博朋克2077、幻影自由。图片来源：CD Projekt Red。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cyberpunk-2077-Phantom-Liberty-cyberware-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3501142" class="wp-caption-text">赛博朋克2077、幻影自由。图片来源：CD Projekt Red。</figcaption></figure><p>更新 2.0 在间谍惊悚片主题扩展<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/cyberpunk-2077-phantom-liberty-launch-timezone-console-pc-3499805">《幻影自由》</a></em>之前发布，将所罗门·里德（伊德里斯·艾尔巴饰演）引入游戏。</p><p> “V 的间谍速成课程有着扣人心弦的情节，如果你喜欢原版游戏的主要故事，你一定会喜欢这个，”安迪·布朗说道，他赞扬了狗镇新区域的增加以及其余的变化。随更新而来。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-legend-of-zelda-tears-of-the-kingdom">《塞尔达传说：王国之泪》</a></em>可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tears-of-the-kingdom-player-completes-the-game-without-touching-hyrule-3503794">在不接触海拉尔表面的情况下</a>被击败，尽管这位玩家花了一些时间才实现这一目标。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-apologises-for-anti-russian-comments-found-in-phantom-liberty-3504214">《赛博朋克 2077》开发者为《幻影自由》中发现的反俄罗斯评论道歉，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
帕拉莫尔预告将于本周四登陆的新产品https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-tease-something-new-landing-this-thursday-3504220?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paramore-tease-something-new-landing-this-thursdayCharlotte Krol Tue, 26 Sep 2023 09:00:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop-punkRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3504220 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕拉莫尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>下个月还有两个日期已列出</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-tease-something-new-landing-this-thursday-3504220">帕拉莫尔 (Paramore) 的帖子预告了本周四的新内容，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕拉莫尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/paramore-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>开玩笑说有新东西将于本周四（9 月 28 日）登陆。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/paramore-cover-interview-2023-this-is-why-3396051">帕拉莫尔——“我希望没有年轻女性经历我所做的事情”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（9 月 25 日）乐队分享了一段在苹果 Notes 应用程序中编写的文字屏幕录制内容，开头是：“Re.这就是为什么。”</p><p>该说明随后列出了三个明显的日期——“9.28”（9月28日）、“10.2”（10月2日）和“10.6”（10月6日）——并分别针对这些日期列出了以下三个短语：“这就是原因” ，“这是为什么？”，“这是为什么吗？”。</p><p>粉丝们很快就猜测这张纸条可能意味着什么。有人认为这三个乐句是乐队最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/paramore-this-is-why-album-review-3393080">《This Is Why》</a>发行后几个月内出现的 B 面标题。</p><p> “bside来了？ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f633.png" alt="😳" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ，”一位歌迷问道，而另一位歌迷则声称他们上个月预测乐队正在准备 B 面——尽管未经证实。请参阅下面的最后一篇文章。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我确实预测到了这一点，你无法向我隐瞒任何事情，帕拉莫尔<a href="https://t.co/gEM1e9oiwV">pic.twitter.com/gEM1e9oiwV</a></p><p> — 埃拉 (@ellxsimpson) <a href="https://twitter.com/ellxsimpson/status/1706340619675668908?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 25 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此前，Paramore 歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">海莉·威廉姆斯 (Hayley Williams)</a>上个月透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-williams-reveals-paramore-are-back-in-the-studio-3489968">乐队已经回到录音室</a>。</p><p>他们最近提前结束了北美巡演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-cancel-remaining-north-american-tour-dates-due-to-illness-3481115">由于威廉姆斯的肺部感染，最后的演出被取消</a>。威廉姆斯在德克萨斯州休斯顿的一场演出中生病后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-postpone-san-francisco-show-sickness-3472273">乐队推迟了四场现场演出</a>，并提前结束了巡演。</p><p> 8 月，乐队在 Instagram 上分享了工作室照片，威廉姆斯在 Discord 上确认他们确实正在创作新音乐。</p><p> “我们已经离开公路好几个星期了……主要是在洛杉矶。值得庆幸的是，我们有一些休息时间，但我们也投入了一些工作，”她告诉粉丝。 “回到工作室感觉很好。一旦我们回到纳什维尔，就会有更多这样的事情。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cwd9GDTpL9r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 56